About Us
/$
$
Roomers, located next to Generations restaurant, on Main Street is the number one place to experience nightlife in downtown Lake Placid. With nightly drink specials, a DJ playing your favorite hits, with a welcoming and friendly staff, you are guaranteed a safe and fun experience full of dancing, bar games, and TVs to enjoy your favorite sporting events. We look forward to having you.
/$
